aces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢send request個到header有個位叫x-lihkg-digest<br />\n後面個value係要計出嚟<br />\n如果拆到計digest個function出嚟比自己個crawler用<br />\n應該就可以任fetch唔嬲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4FPQDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4FPQDD.png&h=8ff8163e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一係就好似我依加咁 每fetch一次等2~3秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e95cd6cb3e51629b5cfe1a49028f37abcc9baa6c","tid":2367593,"uid":287326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"補充個crawler係無問題<br />\n<br />\n係想知點樣avoid call得太多比連狗ban既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}